@startuml SD-06
skinparam backgroundColor #FAFAFA
skinparam roundcorner 10
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam sequenceArrowThickness 1.5
skinparam sequenceLifeLineBorderColor #888888
skinparam sequenceParticipantBorderColor #444444
skinparam sequenceParticipantFontSize 12
skinparam sequenceMessageFontSize 11

title SD-06: Feedback Salah & Auto-Learning

actor "Pengunjung\n(Browser)" as User #4A90D9
participant "Laravel\n(ChatbotController)" as Laravel #2E8B57
participant "ChatbotService\n(Laravel)" as Service #50C878
database "MySQL\n(Database)" as DB #3498DB
participant "Flask\n(app.py)" as Flask #E67E22
participant "ChatbotTrainer\n(trainer.py)" as Trainer #9B59B6

== 1. User Klik Salah dan Koreksi ==
User -> Laravel : POST /feedback\n{user_message: "dimana poli gigi?",\nis_correct: false,\ncorrect_room_name: "Poli Gigi"}
activate Laravel

== 2. Simpan Feedback Salah ==
Laravel -> Service : saveFeedback(data)
activate Service
Service -> DB : ChatbotFeedback::create({\nis_correct: 0,\ncorrect_room_name: "Poli Gigi",...})
activate DB
DB --> Service : feedback tersimpan
deactivate DB

== 3. Update Kata Kunci Ruangan ==
Service -> DB : Cari ruangan bernama "Poli Gigi"
activate DB
DB --> Service : ditemukan DataRuangan(id=8)
deactivate DB

Service -> DB : Tambah kata kunci baru:\nkata_kunci += "dimana poli gigi"
activate DB
DB --> Service : kata_kunci diperbarui
deactivate DB

note over Service
  needSync = true
  Trigger sinkronisasi model AI
end note

== 4. Sinkronisasi Otomatis (Auto-Learning) ==
Service -> DB : Ambil semua DataRuangan\n(id, nama, gedung, keyword, dll)
activate DB
DB --> Service : list semua ruangan
deactivate DB

Service -> DB : Ambil feedback benar\nuntuk data training tambahan
activate DB
DB --> Service : list feedback
deactivate DB

Service -> Flask : POST /sync\n{rooms: [...], feedbacks: [...],\nintent_feedbacks: [...]}
activate Flask

== 5. Retraining Model AI ==
Flask -> Trainer : train_rooms(rooms, feedbacks)
activate Trainer
note right of Trainer
  Encode ulang semua ruangan (S-BERT)
  Tambah feedback baru ke training data
  Simpan modelDataRuangan.pkl
end note
Trainer --> Flask : rooms_ok = true
deactivate Trainer

Flask -> Trainer : train_intent(intent_feedbacks)
activate Trainer
note right of Trainer
  Gabung data label baru
  Latih ulang SVM classifier
  Simpan modelLabel.pkl
end note
Trainer --> Flask : intent_ok = true
deactivate Trainer

Flask -> Flask : svc.reload()\n(muat ulang model baru)

Flask --> Service : {success: true,\nmessage: "Sinkronisasi selesai"}
deactivate Flask

Service --> Laravel : {status: "success"}
deactivate Service

== 6. Konfirmasi ke User ==
Laravel --> User : JSON {status: "success"}
deactivate Laravel

note over User
  Browser tampilkan:
  "Terima kasih! Jawaban Anda membantu
  chatbot belajar lebih baik."
end note

@enduml
